b) 100,000
c) 340,000
d) All the rest of Israel

1 Chronicles 13 — The Ark Brought from Kiriath-Jearim
41. According to 1 Chronicles 13:3, David said, “Let us bring again the ark of our God to us, for we did not seek it in the days of whom?”
