c) Samuel
d) Solomon

70. According to 1 Chronicles 17:14, “I will confirm him in my house and in my kingdom forever and his throne shall be established forever.” This points ultimately to whom?
a) Solomon
b) The Messiah (Jesus Christ)
c) Hezekiah
d) Josiah

