b) Hadad
c) Rezon
d) Hezion

74. According to 1 Chronicles 18:4, David took from Hadadezer how many chariots?
a) 500
b) 1,000
c) 7,000
d) 10,000

75. According to 1 Chronicles 18:6, the Lord gave victory to David wherever he went. What did David put in Damascus (Aram) indicating subjugation?
