138. According to 2 Chronicles 1:11-12, God said to Solomon, “Because this was in your heart, and you have not asked for possessions, wealth, honor, or the life of your enemies, but have asked for wisdom and knowledge to govern my people, therefore wisdom and knowledge are granted to you. I will also give you what?”
a) A long life
b) Riches, possessions, and honor such as none of the kings before you had
